				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I'm sorry but this sword is hardly inferior to the Razing Sword mentioned several posts ago.<BR>
<BR>
This sword will do the same damage (20) but you will hit nearly one half second faster with this sword than with the Razing Sword (36 dly vs. 40 dly).  This is not the best sword in the game, in terms of buffs, but it is very damage efficient.<BR>
<BR>
And Soulfire, for all you &quot;there are too many Pally only weapons&quot; types out there..  23dam 45dly and five charges of Complete Heal?  Big Deal.  I have been all over the Everlore boards and not seen very many owners of Soulfire who are satisfied customers.  I'm not saying you guys aren't out there... but with new zones opening and new loot being dropped, Soulfire is more of a status symbol nowadays.<BR>
<BR>
-Soliyan, Lvl 22 Paladin - Karana
